
'hkLink' builds links in keywords with Hatena Keyword Auto Link API.


  Hatena Keyword Auto Link API
    http://d.hatena.ne.jp/keyword/%a4%cf%a4%c6%a4%ca%a5%ad%a1%bc%a5%ef%a1%bc%a5%c9%bc%ab%c6%b0%a5%ea%a5%f3%a5%afAPI
  Hatena Keyword API
    http://d.hatena.ne.jp/keyword/%a4%cf%a4%c6%a4%ca%a5%ad%a1%bc%a5%ef%a1%bc%a5%c9API

  see also:
    http://watcher.moe-nifty.com/memo/2004/06/api_1.html
    http://watcher.moe-nifty.com/memo/2004/07/api.html



xmlRPC libraries are necessary for building this application.

  xmlRPC: 
    http://github.com/tsupo/xmlRPC/tree
